$ Visual Studio GUI

table { lll
    ☰ ☰ typical location
  Editor window ☰ editing content of code file ☰ center
  Solution explorer ☰ displays of projects, solutions and their code files  ☰ top right
  Output windows ☰ compiler messages, Visual Studio notifications, publishing status messages etc. ☰ bottom center
  Team explorer ☰ track work items, connnect to → development/version-control-systems[version control systems] (Git, TFVC) ☰ bottom right
table }


